{"id":32,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":32,"title":"Guide to the Friend","subtitle":"","short_title":"Guide to the Friend","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Guide to the",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],[".title","Possible Ideas for Family Home Evening"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.f1"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","Read President Henry B. Eyring’s message",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/05/an-unshakable-foundation.p1"},"“An Unshakable Foundation”"],"(pages 2–3). Take a trip outside to look at the foundation of your own house or a nearby building. Then talk about why a good foundation is important and make a list of ways you can create your own “foundation of faith.”"]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/05/1-2-3-were-here-to-help.p1"},"“1-2-3! We’re Here to Help!”"],"(pages 4–5). As a family, make thank-you cards for someone who has helped you with the things you need."]],["li",["span.label","3."],[".para","What do you know about your family history? Turn to",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/05/i-can-climb-my-family-tree.p1"},"“I Can Climb My Family Tree!”"],"(page 22) and fill out the chart together."]],["li",["span.label","4."],[".para","Read the story",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/05/the-princess-and-the-monster.p1"},"“The Princess and the Monster”"],"(pages 26–27). Talk about the importance of including everyone and then play a game together as a family."]],["li",["span.label","5."],[".para","Use the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/05/prophets-teach-us-to-live-the-restored-gospel.p1"},"Bringing Primary Home"],"lesson and activity to learn more about this month’s Primary theme (pages 40–41)."]]]]],[".resources",[".moreInfo",[".title","Hidden CTR Ring"],["div",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p9"},"Did you find the ring? Look on page 35!"]],[".moreInfo",["div",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p10"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"can be found on the Internet at",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend"},"lds.org/friend"],". To subscribe online, go to",["a",{"href":"http://store.lds.org"},"store.lds.org"],"."]],[".moreInfo",["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p11"},"To send us a letter, drawing, or poem, please fill out this form and include it with your submission. Please also include a school photo or high-quality snapshot. Submissions will not be returned and may be edited for length and clarity. Children whose work is submitted should be at least three years old."],["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p12"},["span.emphasis","Please send your submission to:"]],[".address",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Magazine"],[".address","50 E. North Temple St., Rm. 2432"],[".address","Salt Lake City, UT 84150-0024"],[".address",["span.emphasis","Or email:"],["a",{"href":"mailto:friend@ldschurch.org"},"friend@ldschurch.org"]],["div",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p17"},["span.emphasis","The following information and permission must be included:"]],["div",{"id":"p18","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p18"},"Full name____________________"],["div",{"id":"p19","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p19"},"Age__________________________"],["div",{"id":"p20","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p20"},"State/Province, Country______________________"],["div",{"id":"p21","uri":"/friend/2013/05/guide-to-the-friend.p21"},["span.emphasis","I agree to the terms of the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Submission Agreement (",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend/parentalconsent"},"lds.org/friend/parentalconsent"],") and grant permission for the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"to print my child’s submission and photo in print or online."],"__________________